                  <summary>I) Dәrsanä Rufāʾel “Homily on Raphael” (fols. 4ra-50ra) &#xD;
II) Taʾāmra Rufāʾel “Miracles of Raphael”: 6 Miracles (fols. 50ra-66vb)&#xD;
